      <p>The YieldMax Ultra Option Income Strategy ETF (ULTY) employs a <strong>multi-asset covered call strategy</strong> that differentiates it from single-stock focused funds like MSTY. Instead of targeting one company, ULTY dynamically allocates across a basket of high-volatility stocks, writing covered calls to harvest maximum option premiums.</p>
      
      <p>This approach allows ULTY to capitalize on volatility spikes across multiple sectors simultaneously. When meme stocks surge, AI companies crater, or biotech names experience clinical trial results, ULTY positions itself to collect premium from whichever names exhibit the highest implied volatility.</p>
      
