        <h3>⚠️ Critical Understanding Required</h3>
        <p>ULTY's 134% yield is <strong>not sustainable income</strong>. The 7,003% payout ratio means distributions consist primarily of <strong>return of capital</strong> - essentially giving you your own money back while the share price declines. This is a momentum income play, not a long-term wealth builder.</p>
